👉 Spring Framework is a Java framework that helps you build applications easily by managing objects and their dependencies for you.

🧠 In Simple Words
Instead of you doing:

Creating objects ❌
Managing dependencies ❌
Wiring everything manually ❌

👉 Spring does it for you ✅

Benefits:
1. Loose coupling
2. Boilerplate code
3. Maintainability and scalable

| Concept     | Role in Spring                  |
| ----------- | ------------------------------- |
| IoC         | Spring controls object creation |
| DI          | Spring injects dependencies     |
| Beans       | Objects managed by Spring       |
| Annotations | Configure everything easily     |

👉 Spring = NestJS (Java version 😄)

Controllers → same
Services → same
DI → same

